{"tid":1587240,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"攬炒巴團隊facebook post得9個like","createTime":"2019-09-22T10:19:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T06:48:11.000Z","uid":179963,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c4c5a99a969b93c15a2113a80eca9a925a3b2414","tid":1587240,"uid":179963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T10:19:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HRhhtLC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHRhhtLC.png&h=974aaa4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好撚嬲，又話和理非國際戰線點點點<br />\n其實就當真係做緊嘢嘅人喺condom<br />\n膠post圍爐就多，正經嘢唔做。<br />\ntwitter國際戰線黎黎去去都係果幾十個人推post<br />\n<br />\n求下大家，可唔可以當抗爭喺考會考，考dse咁樣<br />\n有目標咁去努力去衝，做到真正嘅全民參與。<br />\n每日搭車，等車，食飯時抽時間，當做功課咁做，好唔好？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個channel有每日要推個twitter post整合，唔洗用腦禁入去推就得<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBj632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=862ab2e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n<br />\n攬炒巴團隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standwithhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandwithhk%2F&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBj632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=c02da063\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standwithhk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStand_with_HK&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBj632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=506424dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK</a>"},{"pid":"81d67c75769c324082a3ed91491297881756c1ac","tid":1587240,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T10:20:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"91e5a1